The Energy and Petroleum Regulatory Authority (Epra) has also increased the price of a litre of diesel and kerosene by Sh5.51 and Sh5.32, respectively, with the changes taking effect from midnight. Motorists are set for a tough few weeks as the price of a litre of super petrol has shot up by Sh8.19 in the monthly review by the energy regulator. 

The Energy and Petroleum Regulatory Authority (Epra) has also increased the price of a litre of diesel and kerosene by Sh5.51 and Sh5.32, respectively, with the changes taking effect from midnight. 



